title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
OB: PA (8/17/01 2:03:29 PM): When you export a directory (project) and place the exported JAR in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when you overwrite the exported JAR file for the second time.
EB: The system should not display an out of sync message when overwriting the exported JAR file in the same directory.
SR: To reproduce: 1. Export a directory (project). 2. Place the exported JAR in the same directory (project). 3. Overwrite the exported JAR file for the second time. Observe the out of sync message.
